summary: NEW YORK, April 30, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- The Nasdaq Stock Market announced today that it will delist the Class A common stock of Alpine 4 Holdings, Inc. Alpine 4 Holdings, Inc.’s stock was suspended on October 18, 2024 and has not traded on Nasdaq since that time. Nasdaq also announced today that it will delist the common stock of Orgenesis Inc.
